<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Gaming Website</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
      background-color: #2b2b2b; /* Slightly lighter background */
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #1e1e1e; /* Darker header */
      padding: 15px 0;
    }

    nav {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .section {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background-color: #353535; /* Slightly lighter section background */
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    button {
      padding: 15px 30px;
      font-size: 24px;
      border: none;
      background-color: #ff4d00;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #ff6600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to the Gaming Universe! Your lucky number is <%= diceValue %> </h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="#">Home</a>
      <a href="#">Games</a>
      <a href="#">About</a>
      <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>We are passionate gamers, dedicated to bringing you the best gaming experience. Our mission is to provide a platform for gamers to connect and enjoy the world of gaming.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Featured Game</h2>
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800" alt="Featured Game">
      <p>Experience the thrilling world of our featured game. Join us and embark on an exciting gaming adventure.</p>
      <button>Play Now</button>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Have any questions or suggestions? Feel free to reach out to us through our contact form or email. We'd love to hear from you!</p>
      <button>Contact</button>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
